      <h1>Sorting Search Results</h1>
      <?CHUNK filename="help/contact-us.chnk" optional="1"?>
      <p>Sorting is available for most results lists, though the sort options
            may vary per collection, and all sorting is limited the maximum
            sort threshold allowed by the system (1000 items). In the upper right hand corner
            of the search results by item display you will see either a menu of sort
            options, or a message indicating that the threshold has been exceeded.
            If you see that the threshold has been exceeded, try using the "revise
            this search" link to add more terms to the search in hopes of retrieving
            a smaller result. </p>
